  "title": "System Engineer ($5500/East)",
  "description": "<p><strong>System Engineer</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>·         Administer and support Microsoft 365 services and on-prem:</li><li>·        Exchange Online, SharePoint Online, OneDrive, Microsoft Teams</li><li>·         Windows server OS administration, Active directory administration and migration</li><li>·        Microsoft exchange server , SCCM and WSUS</li><li>·         Implement and manage Microsoft Intune (MDM/MAM):</li><li>·         Device compliance policies, configuration profiles, apps deployment</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>3–6 years of experience in Microsoft 365 administration</li><li>Proven experience working in a Managed Services / MSP environment</li><li>Strong hands-on experience with Microsoft Intune</li><li>Experience with SaaS / email migrations</li><li>Familiar with Microsoft Copilot for Microsoft 365 (deployment or support experience  preferred)</li><li>Knowledge of Windows, macOS, iOS, Android device management</li><li>Good understanding of Entra ID</li><li>Strong troubleshooting, communication, and documentation skills</li></ul><p><br />*Only shortlisted candidates will be notified*<br /></p><p>Please submit your updated resume in MS format by using the <strong>APPLY NOW BUTTON.</strong></p><p>Alternatively, you may also email your resume to us at <a href=\"mailto:emily.fong@atomrecruit.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>emily.fong@atomrecruit.com</strong></a></p><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>Emily Fong</strong><br /><strong>Senior Talent Specialist\n</strong>Atomrecruit Pte. Ltd. | MOM EA License No.: 15C7443\nEA Personnel Reg No.: R</p><p>1768368</p>",
